<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.2">
<l>niṇantā ṉuruki nilantā ṉaṉaippa neṭumpaṟ kuḻikaṭpēy</l>
<l>tuṇaṅkai yeṟintu cūḻu nōkkiccuṭalai naviḻt teṅkum</l>
<l>kaṇaṅkaḷ kūṭip piṇaṅkaṇ māntik kaḷitta maṉattavā</l>
<l>yaṇaṅku kāṭṭi laṉalkai yēnti yaḻaka ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wherever, while the fat melts [and] wets the ground long-toothed,</l>
<l>hollow-eyed demonesses vigorously dance the Tuṇaṅkai, look all around</l>
<l>[and] extinguish the pyres, as the troupes gather, eating corpses, being joyous of mind</l>
<l>on the frightful creation ground hand raised with fire the beautiful one dances.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
